    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i>Is it Glitched? Or programmed that way?</i></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2158220/extras/fec866aaa1bd495caaf76b389ea6c58c.avif?t=1771072188\" width=614 height=160 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2158220/extras/b75e7d8c311a69b5a8d026211d0edffc.poster.avif?t=1771072188\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2158220/extras/b75e7d8c311a69b5a8d026211d0edffc.webm?t=1771072188\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2158220/extras/b75e7d8c311a69b5a8d026211d0edffc.mp4?t=1771072188\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Play as a girl robot called Glitch and save a strange universe from an impending apocalypse. </i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><i>IMPORTANT: This game is intended to be very difficult. You will likely die over and over again. Only play if you're a pro-gamer, else you'll end up uninstalling in rage. </i></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3D Platformer gameplay with ragdoll physics. Different worlds full of dangerous hazards such as traps, obstacles, and hazards</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Character customization - customize your character with different outfits, weapons, stat builds etc.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Visit multiple other worlds with their own characters, NPCs and enemies. Discover and unlock new items, defeat enemies, complete NPC quests and discover secrets. Complete NPC quests and boss battles.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Physics-based gameplay - You'll need to use not just your timing and jumping to traverse these dangerous worlds, but ragdoll skills to tumble yourself across hazards and other threats</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >souls like gameplay</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2158220/extras/3d6a76961c0a249af139c7740cb334a2.poster.avif?t=1771072188\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2158220/extras/3d6a76961c0a249af139c7740cb334a2.webm?t=1771072188\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2158220/extras/3d6a76961c0a249af139c7740cb334a2.mp4?t=1771072188\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2158220/extras/0f0b51bc98eb0797e67fb0ee3c2590eb.avif?t=1771072188\" width=614 height=160 /></span></p>",
